{"tid":2069653,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你真係明白嚟緊立法會選舉會發生咩事？","createTime":"2020-06-18T14:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:56:40.000Z","uid":7542,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13dc338908b45c1338a4813eb0a3d6afb6753dd7","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"身邊有好多人都仲喺度覺得，上年嘅區議會選舉嗰種投票氛圍可以帶到落去嚟緊嘅立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真係咩？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n分析咗<ins><strong>多個國家</strong></ins>嘅案例之後，我嘅總結係：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嚟緊立法會，我哋將會墮落到變成非洲獨裁國家扮民主嘅選舉</span></strong>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或者等我簡單解釋一下今次立法會選舉會發生咩事 </span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共截至現時為止，至少有<strong><ins>4招</ins></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1）<strong>DQ</strong>：政府已經放晒風，如果你係反對國安法，或者支持拉布作為議會抗爭，都可以成為DQ理由。即係調返轉，如果泛民主派任何候選人唔係支持國安法，同埋反對議會進行激烈抗爭，入閘機會都十分渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n2) <strong>票站監控</strong>：選管會已經話今次嘅立法會票站入面，會設有攝錄鏡頭監視情況。你覺得冇乜嘢？有啲人買票，就係靠監視鏡頭去對投票者進行施壓。如果我大膽推測，有唔少中資機構或者同鄉會可能用類似手段，恐嚇其實佢哋頭咩票上面係會知道。<br />\n<br />\n3) <strong>監票受阻</strong>：如果監票過程，只要有少少人出聲表達不滿，票站主任就可以即時終止點票，並且驅逐相關人士離開。你可以想像，即係懷疑選舉不公嘅一方，最後反而冇辦法繼續監察點票過程。<br />\n<br />\n4) <strong>警察監場</strong>：我明白咁講會俾人鬧，但係其實上次區議會選舉期間，啲毫無紀律嘅紀律部隊係比較克制。但係經歷咗咁多嘢之後，今次立法會選舉佢哋睇嚟係唔會抗拒直接介入、甚至粗暴干預過程。邊個可以確保到佢哋唔會喺票站入面發癲、唔會喺票站附近截查後生仔、唔會喺選舉日阻礙民主派拉票？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我上邊講嘅四點，係基於呢幾日嘅新聞，同埋<strong>分析咗幾十個國家嘅選舉情況之後得出嘅</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上邊講嘅每一件事，係真真實實咁喺其他專制國家發生過。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【選舉操控】9招令親中派全取議席 🎯 | 秘密武器4分鐘變廢票 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=6a70900a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n^今次呢條片，由睇完本書去到剪好條片用咗三個星期，差啲想放棄。不過呢個題目真係好值得做，希望呢條片可以幫到大家預備一下，嚟緊嘅立法會選舉有咩最惡劣嘅情況可以出現！<strong>可悲嘅係，我哋好似一一應驗緊</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">希望大家可以click入條片，CLSS，撳個鐘仔。支持 Tat Talk 更多類似嘅片，或者留言俾啲靈感/意見我！</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em><ins>點解想整個咁嘅 YouTube Channel？</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n好多時候睇網上面嘅 commentator youtuber，蕭生世良陶傑沈旭暉等，會引經據典講好多歷史事件，但係佢哋只能夠蜻蜓點水。<br />\n<br />\n希望長遠可以建立到呢一個頻道，傳播知識。尤其是填補返好多人唔知道嘅歷史空白，做好一切思想準備。Outmaneuver them.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*歡迎大家討論一下，尤其係如果睇完條片有啲唔明，我都會逐一解答！"},{"pid":"1f05eed1f3f9c5adbc542f2b271f2e338e9be959","tid":2069653,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fc97ffb78280a115dd8432aa51653f71635f8d","tid":2069653,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"見後生去票站就拉番狗屋搞你24小時 反正冇成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd871efe1c17c2961286294eccebf9ba1cc7b7a","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57fc97ffb78280a115dd8432aa51653f71635f8d","tid":2069653,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"見後生去票站就拉番狗屋搞你24小時 反正冇成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"片嘅 4:10 ，斯里蘭卡選舉就係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n用警察搞鳩你反對派政黨、參選人同埋支持者<br />\n<br />\n選舉當日無端端爆門衝入政黨嘅辦公室 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6845e28fa6ca5291066453ae16b3bb43850b9ec","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"輕輕 push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67db29787fa234a5e64785d89583290620f3875","tid":2069653,"uid":142153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb818f90da1b8834eaeef9c753186bdbc25d14d9","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f05eed1f3f9c5adbc542f2b271f2e338e9be959","tid":2069653,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c36c6276c446caa91a61b8b0961ef1bd3cd733","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67db29787fa234a5e64785d89583290620f3875","tid":2069653,"uid":142153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"學術台原來都有絲打幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432bd955ad95c06ba4f88ab6c0f649e6a36fa70f","tid":2069653,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f037d72dd0a7bb8c571941cec84db1633cd427e","tid":2069653,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba14c10187cfc58d0fdaeafb3296ec45cb9939a","tid":2069653,"uid":180124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"反正都係架啦<br />\n你對個立會仲抱咩希望？<br />\n想要35+？<br />\n總之投左想投既人<br />\n但結局就係佢一定唔會比你35+"},{"pid":"d68ff25c33953ce8dd6f9471ac91f00d1ec92b82","tid":2069653,"uid":71564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"樓主講既好有可能發生<br />\n只係泛民班舊電池仲諗緊點做忠誠反對派<br />\n一啲反抗意志都無<br />\n我諗用dq一招已經夠做了<br />\n好似當年dq曬本土派咁<br />\n<br />\nbtw黃營連初選都未傾掂<br />\n玩下手話唔認初選然後自己出黎選<br />\n只會變咗上次新西咁俾何妖入場"},{"pid":"0415950f6bce00fe1a50c9bde105e1684487c3a6","tid":2069653,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49998a2052eb23b73ea87230c532e7230b3ca5e0","tid":2069653,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa87b4e11e81d86bfb2566ea1708b44b16d19ff","tid":2069653,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"老老實實係就希望光明正大做<br />\n好似馬拉咁黑房然後多左個票箱呢啲就最好<br />\n啲西方民主國家對選舉舞弊仲緊張過被自殺掟落街"},{"pid":"241d99387d9b79fb37a9b3adaf34364a10099842","tid":2069653,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"漏左利用制度配票同種票<br />\n仲有名單比例代表制之下只要有反對派聯合初選就可以達到0界票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2055907/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2055907/page/1</a><br />\n我之前都開過post"},{"pid":"4f5b371f9a86f61ac5e1c7fa04d6bb16c5892835","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241d99387d9b79fb37a9b3adaf34364a10099842","tid":2069653,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"漏左利用制度配票同種票<br />\n仲有名單比例代表制之下只要有反對派聯合初選就可以達到0界票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2055907/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2055907/page/1</a><br />\n我之前都開過post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"我參考嘅嗰一本書入面其實都有講過配票呢一樣野，但係因為始終佢太過 specific 放喺每一個地方都有啲唔同，所以我就冇 cover啦~<br />\n<br />\n至於種票，其實入面都有輕輕帶過，例如烏克蘭選舉亦都有死人投票嘅情況！<br />\n<br />\nBtw 等我睇吓巴打個 post 先！"},{"pid":"43613acca1fdea202f852a61f25242cf34bf3b06","tid":2069653,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"432bd955ad95c06ba4f88ab6c0f649e6a36fa70f","tid":2069653,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"唔使灰心嘅，好多時極權政府自己做完啲嘢好似係市民受苦。但係睇得多你就會發現，唔知點解政權係會有一定程度嘅報應。<br />\n<br />\n只係時辰未到姐～"}]}